## ðŸš€ What Forward Array Does

Forward Array currently:

- Polls price data on a schedule and saves it locally
- Updates positions / gains using the latest prices
- Computes portfolio-level metrics (PnL and related stats)
- Keeps a local log so everything still works offline

This project will grow over time as I learn more about Python, automation, and system design.

